**Backend:**
- Uses DRF generics (ListCreateAPIView, RetrieveAPIView, etc.)
- Custom permission class extending DjangoModelPermissions
- Service layer abstraction (services.py files)
- ThreadPoolExecutor for background tasks (2 workers)
- 202 ACCEPTED responses for async operations
- Django Solo pattern for singleton settings
- Regex validation in serializers
- Permission groups via django-page-perms

**Frontend:**
- Nuxt 3 with TypeScript
- Composables for state management (useAuth, useApi, usePagePerms, useNavigation)
- Page permission checking via middleware
- Multiple view modes (kanban/table) with state persistence
- Filter state management with watchers
- Inline editing with optimistic updates
- Modal forms with validation
- Batch operations with dropdown menus
- Relative time formatting utilities

**Testing:**
- pytest with pytest-django
- Factory pattern for test data (UserFactory, RepoFactory)
- Fixture-based auth with group/permission setup
